eadline.com/2012/05/glees-brad-buecker-to-helm-lionsgate-summit-tuner-time-after-time-266705/|date=4 May 2012|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=22 May 2017}}</ref><ref>{{IMDb title|tt2391085|title=Time After Time}}</ref> * ''[[James Bobin|Tribyville]]'' (TBA)<ref>{{cite web|last=Foreman|first=Liza|title='Muppets,' 'Ali G' Director James Bobin Signs on for 'Tribyville' Musical (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/movies/column-post/disney-talks-period-musical-tribleyville-exclusive-69446|publisher=The Wrap|accessdate=3 January 2013}}</ref><ref>{{IMDb title|tt2599006|title=Tribyville}}</ref> * ''Untitled [[Barry Manilow]] project'' (TBA)<ref>{{cite web|last=Flores|first=Ramses|title=Michael Stipe and Tom Hanks to Develop Barry Manilow 'Musical'|url=http://collider.com/michael-stipe-and-tom-hanks-to-develop-barry-manilow-musical/|date=10 September 2009|publisher=Collider|accessdate=17 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{IMDb title|tt1512261|title=Untitled Barry Manilow Project}}</ref> * ''Untitled [[Byron Janis]] project'' (biographical, TBA)<ref>{{cite web|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Martin Scorsese Developing Byron Janis Biopic at Paramount (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/martin-scorsese-producing-byron-janis-biopic-paramount-1201674748/|date=7 January 2016|publisher=Variety|accessdate=18 January 2017}}</ref><ref>{{IMDb title|tt5337206|title=Untitled Bryon Janis Project}}</ref> * ''[[Brian Yorkey#Film and television|Untitled Fashion Musical]]'' (TBA)<ref name="developedidea"/><ref>{{IMDb title|tt8064858|title=Untitled Fashion Musical Project}}</ref> * ''Untitled [[Grateful Dead]] musical project'' (TBA)<ref>{{cite web|last=Fleming Jr|first=Mike|title=The Grateful Dead 'Truckin' On Music-Driven Feature Film Package|url=http://deadline.com/2011/11/the-grateful-dead-gets-truckin-on-music-driven-feature-film-package-196772/|accessdate=5 November 2017|website=Deadline Hollywood|date=18 November 2011}}</ref><ref>{{IMDb title|tt2121384|title=Untitled Gratef